article_title: United Healthcare remains an option for Valley health plan shoppers – for now
article_text:
Largest insurer in country says it can’t commit to ACA in 2017

Covered California says United has contract for 2016

Consumers have until Jan. 31 to choose coverage

article_metadata.news-keywords: Covered California, Fresno, Madera, Kings, United Healthcare, Health Net, Peter V. Lee, Affordable Care Act
article_metadata.description: Health consumers in Fresno, Kings and Madera counties who are enrolling in health plans through the state’s insurance exchange may have noticed two new options – United Healthcare and Health Net.
